="https://www.nme.com/games/overwatch"><em>《守望先锋》</em></a>的消亡。</p><p>其他消息方面，有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/death-stranding"><em>《死亡搁浅》</em></a>创作的纪录片<em>《小岛秀夫：连接世界》</em>现已确定在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/death-stranding-documentary-gets-disney-release-date-3585971">发布的正式日期</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-overwatch-2-update-will-hopefully-revitalise-the-game-3585987">新的“守望先锋 2”更新有望“重振”该游戏，该游戏</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
